qa_package: qa_test_suse-cert

=====================================

[introduction]
A network testing tools, for downloading testing.

[require packages]
gcc-c++
hwinfo-devel
coreutils
bonnie
cdrecord
mkisofs
wget
e2fsprogs
util-linux
build
mgetty
pure-ftpd
python

[what the test does]
Default setting of this test suite is to download a 400MB file from specify ftp site for certain times.

[what happens ]
A file named 400MB with size of exactly 400MB will be downloaded 20 times to /tmp by default.

[common problems]
Depends on network b
bandwidth downloading process could be slow or even broken.

[things to take care of]
Make sure there are enough disk space in SUT.
